<div class = 'row'>
<div class = 'span10'>
<div id = "demo_frame">
<h1>Put the blocks in the right day and the right time of day.</h1><br /><br />

<p>1) All three days had at least one block<br />

2) No block arrived on Monday evening or Wednesday evening<br />

3) J and N arrived on the same day<br />

4) L arrived 3 time slots before M and before J<br />

5) K was the third block to arrive<br />

6) M and N arrived in the afternoon<br />

7) No time of day has more than one block<br /></p>

<div style = "height:350px;width:480px;margin-bottom:-230px;">
<div class="draggable" id = "J">
	<p>J</p>
</div>
<div class="draggable" id = "K">
	<p>K</p>
</div>
<div class="draggable" id = "L">
	<p>L</p>
</div>
<div class="draggable" id = "M">
	<p>M</p>
</div>
<div class="draggable" id = "N">
	<p>N</p>
</div><br />
</div>

